com.palomamobile.android.sdk.media

Class JobUploadMedia

  • java.lang.Object
    • Job
      • com.palomamobile.android.sdk.core.qos.BaseRetryPolicyAwareJob<MediaInfo>
        • com.palomamobile.android.sdk.media.BaseJobUploadMedia
          • com.palomamobile.android.sdk.media.JobUploadMedia

  • public class JobUploadMedia
extends BaseJobUploadMedia
    Convenience wrapper around IMediaService.postMedia(String, TypedInput) used to post media that becomes available publicly available. Once this job is completed (with success or failure) it posts EventMediaUploaded on the IEventBus (as returned by ServiceSupport.getEventBus()).
